{"tid":2372851,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"男生被控「大三罷」管有士巴拿 律政司建議守行為 陳炳宙一度不同意 最後下令守行為3年","createTime":"2021-01-20T04:37:50.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-20T10:01:37.000Z","uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ef142d7da7a14a29f8dcc472d47a14523e2b17bb","tid":2372851,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T04:37:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/13067\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F13067&d=CthjHxCXz%2Bl0vOF3eBkmem0Q%2Fwx8zutUsTDhO6XOofs%3D&h=3ed790b0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/13067</a><br />\n<br />\n#粉嶺裁判法院第五庭<br />\n#陳炳宙裁判官<br />\n#審訊 #1111上水 <br />\n<br />\n👤劉(20) <br />\n<br />\n控罪<br />\n(3)管有適合作非法用途的工具<br />\n<br />\n《速報》<br />\n<br />\n控方於開庭時建議給予被告簽保守行為，但陳官不同意，現休庭考慮中⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n簽保$2000，守行為3年，詳情後補。"},{"pid":"3c1516f43d9446f50f07122e6f7648886da3c220","tid":2372851,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T04:38:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b393ad856d0b6a26074085fe5c6713d1f6eb7ed3","tid":2372851,"uid":335434,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T04:40:06.000Z","msg":"即係隻官嫌律政屍太輕手啊!?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49801eb9b59aa81b0ff2adbb1ddae30d31358fde","tid":2372851,"uid":129169,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"b393ad856d0b6a26074085fe5c6713d1f6eb7ed3","tid":2372851,"uid":335434,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T04:40:06.000Z","msg":"即係隻官嫌律政屍太輕手啊!?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T04:40:40.000Z","msg":"係，睇個樣想判監<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" clas